title: Hot Seat Rankings with NFL SuperFriends (Football 8/5)
description:
Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including Tom Brady's contract, D'Onta Foreman being released and Antonio Brown's injury before bringing on John Breech to break down the Hall of Fame enshrinement ceremony and Brinson's coaching hot seat rankings.
